{
  "stem": "93.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the process, we suffered very severe casualties, because the German defense of the Meuse, while not very strong, was sufficient to permit them time to bring heavy forces up to the Moselle River.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when we got to the Moselle River, we ran into a thoroughly entrenched German army, and the fighting was very, very intense.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To make a long story short, we crossed the Moselle River, perhaps the 11th, 12th of September, somewhere in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The dates are not important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from the-- from that date until the end of October of 1944, there was a tremendous battle in which the 317th Infantry in which I served suffered something on the order of 3,000 enlisted men casualties and 188, 190 officer casualties, which in effect meant that the regiment that had started on Omaha Beach had effectively disappeared.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From that battle, which essentially ended in November with the capture of Metz by my division plus others, we then went south and were preparing to cross through the Siegfried Line.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was to have been in December, but it was interrupted by the Battle of the Bulge.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We went north to the Battle of the Bulge, and my division participated in the relief of Bastogne and the subsequent defeat of the German effort that had led to the big bulge that gave the battle its name.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, I have to add that during this dash across France and prior to these big battles, we were introduced to some of the bestiality of which the Germans were capable.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "For instance--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To get back to the original point that I was making, we were introduced to some of the bestiality of which the Germans were capable.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
